atile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-13-726fad2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-13-726fad2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=768%2C574\"><meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"768\"><meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"574\"></div><div><p>Published: <time datetime=\"2021-03-04T14:49:09+00:00\">March 4, 2021 at 2:49 pm</time></p><meta itemprop=\"datePublished\" content=\"2021-03-04T14:49:09+00:00\"><meta itemprop=\"dateModified\" content=\"2021-03-04T14:49:09+00:00\"><p></p></div></div><section itemprop=\"articleBody\"><p>MET has released the Manta MIPS, an update to its existing <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/best-aero-road-helmets-8-tested-and-rated/\">Manta aero road helmet</a>, which it claims is both faster in the wind tunnel, safer and better ventilated than its predecessor.</p><p>The Manta MIPS incorporates a <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/mips-tips-two-things-to-know-when-buying-a-helmet/\">MIPS-C2 brain protection system</a> into the helmet, for improved safety.</p><p>The MIPS system allows the helmet shell to slide 10-15mm relative to the rider’s head in the event of a crash. This is claimed to reduce the rotational force acting on the rider’s brain and, as a result, reduce the risk of injury. It, and other similar technologies, are increasingly being integrated into the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-road-bike-helmets/\">best road bike helmets</a>.</p><div><p><i title=\"Enlarge photo\" data-slide-index=\"1\">Enlarge photo</i></p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 600px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 991px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-M133NR1-b0d263f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960%2C640\" alt=\"MET Manta MIPS\" height=\"639\" width=\"960\"></picture><div><p><i><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><title>icon / camera</title><g fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10 12.08a1.6 1.6 0 1 1 0-3.204 1.6 1.6 0 0 1 0 3.204m0-4.457a2.856 2.856 0 0 0 0 5.711 2.856 2.856 0 0 0 0-5.71\" fill=\"#343434\"></path><path d=\"M16.036 13.23c0 .682-.553 1.234-1.234 1.234H5.199a1.234 1.234 0 0 1-1.234-1.234V7.623c0-.639.518-1.157 1.157-1.157h2.315l.11-.46a1.578 1.578 0 0 1 1.536-1.22h1.837c.734 0 1.37.505 1.537 1.22l.106.46h2.315c.64 0 1.158.518 1.158 1.157v5.607zM10 0C4.478 0 0 4.477 0 10s4.478 10 10 10c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S15.523 0 10 0z\" fill=\"#000\"></path></g></svg></i></p><figcaption><span>MET says the new Manta MIPS aero road helmet has improved safety features and is faster than the competition.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>MET</i></span></p></div></div></div><h2>Marginal gains</h2><p>On top of the safety improvements, MET also claims the Manta MIPS is around 3-4 watts more aerodynamically efficient than both the outgoing Manta and its “average competitors” – which we assume means an average of all the competitor helmets MET tested (meaning individual competitor helmets may be significantly more or less efficient than the average).</p><p>MET declined to say exactly which competitor helmets were tested, but it did say it chose the “best-performing helmets” from four major helmet brands.</p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=354%2C236, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=708%2C472 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1064%2C709 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1418%2C945 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/produ