2C1079 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=554%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1107%2C738 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1661%2C1107 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=554%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1107%2C738 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1661%2C1107 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"MET Manta MIPS wind tunnel\" title=\"met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-21-9001338.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The Manta MIPS was benchmarked in the wind tunnel against the outgoing model and its competitors.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>MET</i></span></p></div><p>The wind tunnel testing was performed at Newton lab in Milan, and tests were performed at zero degrees yaw, at speeds of 33kph, 55kph and 80kph, with each helmet mounted to a fake head for consistent measurements.</p><p>MET tested two head angles that simulate different riding positions: 77 degrees (replicating being sat up on the hoods) and 65 degrees (replicating being hunched down in the drops).</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/fitness-and-training/how-to-ride-faster-without-pedaling-harder/\">How to ride faster without pedaling harder</a></li></ul><p>Ventilation is also said to have been improved over the outgoing version, though MET hasn’t put a figure on the precise level of improvement.</p><p>It nevertheless remains a helmet with minimal venting (the Manta MIPS has 15 vents in total, if you’re counting) due to its focus on aerodynamics, so it’s unlikely to be quite as airy as <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/helmets/road-cycling-helmets/met-trenta-3k-carbon-helmet-review/\">MET’s Trenta 3K Carbon</a>, for example.</p><p>Some trade-off between ventilation and aerodynamics is inevitable for road helmets however, as improving one tends to negatively affect the other.</p><h2>MET Manta MIPS key features</h2><p>Aero and safety concerns aside, the Manta MIPS includes a dedicated <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-sunglasses-for-cycling/\">sunglasses</a> port for storing your favourite shades when you’re not wearing them.</p><p>The chin strap has a Fidlock magnetic buckle and MET also says its fit system is ponytail compatible.</p><div><p><i title=\"Enlarge photo\" data-slide-index=\"1\">Enlarge photo</i></p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 600px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 991px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-sunglasses-ports-942756e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960%2C603\" alt=\"MET Manta MIPS sunglasses port\" height=\"603\" width=\"960\"></picture><div><p><i><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><title>icon / camera</title><g fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10 12.08a1.6 1.6 0 1 1 0-3.204 1.6 1.6 0 0 1 0 3.204m0-4.457a2.856 2.856 0 0 0 0 5.711 2.856 2.856 0 0 0 0-5.71\" fill=\"#343434\"></path><path d=\"M16.036 13.23c0 .682-.553 1.234-1.234 1.234H5.199a1.234 1.234 0 0 1-1.234-1.234V7.623c0-.639.518-1.157 1.157-1.157h2.315l.11-.46a1.578 1.578 0 0 1 1.536-1.22h1.837c.734 0 1.37.505 1.537 1.22l.106.46h2.315c.64 0 1.158.518 1.158 1.157v5.607zM10 0C4.478 0 0 4.477 0 10s4.478 10 10 10c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S15.523 0 10 0z\" fill=\"#000\"></path></g></svg></i></p><figcaption><span>The Manta MIPS has a dedicated sunglasses port at the front of the helmet.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>MET</i></span></p></div></div></div>The Manta MIPS is available in three sizes:<ul><li>Small, 52-56cm, claimed weight 230g</li><li>Medium, 56-58cm, claimed weight 250g</li><li>Large, 58-61cm, claimed weight 270g</li></ul><p>Available in six different colour options, all with reflective rear decals, the MET Manta MIPS has an RRP of €250 / £220 / $300 / AU$400 and is available to purchase now.</p></section><section><h3>Authors</h3><section><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/author/bromleysimon/\"><img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/06/Simon-Bromley_Profile-Pic_2020_04_12_IMG_4585-d34f7eb-scaled.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=60,60\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/06/Simon-Bromley_Profile-Pic_2020_04_12_IMG_4585-d34f7eb-scaled.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=120,120 120w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/06/Simon-Bromley_Profile-Pic_2020_04_12_IMG_4585-d34f7eb-scaled.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=60,60 60w,\" sizes=\"(max-width: 60px) 100vw, 60px\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" alt=\"Simon Bromley_Profile Pic\" title=\"Simon Bromley_Profile Pic_2020_04_12_IMG_4585\"></a><p>Simon is a writer and photographer who has been riding bikes for fun since he was a kid. He took a deep dive into road racing, crits and time trial culture in his twenties, but as a person of very little talent, he always looks to tech to compensate. He loves nothing more than finding a smart (preferably cheap) hack that others hadn’t thought of. His stable of bikes isn’t the most extravagant, but they’re all customised to meet Simon’s particular tastes and kept fastidiously clean.</p></section></section></div>","author":"Simon Bromley","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"957249d6b43634263f3e0f522e77faf6ede114578d4a4bffa00d279c69a33d09","category":"Cycling"}